# Example Tor daemon config for exposing the Axeno relay as an onion service.
# The Rust server intentionally binds to localhost; Tor publishes this hidden service.
#
# Run the relay:
#   AXENO_BIND=127.0.0.1:8787 cargo run
#
# Add this to your torrc, then restart Tor. Read the generated hostname file.

HiddenServiceDir /var/lib/tor/axeno-relay/
HiddenServiceVersion 3
HiddenServicePort 80 127.0.0.1:8787
